name: NONA NANCY 02-03
description: I got an unexpected surprise that made me feel so happy that I didn't have this feeling before. I want to share this happiness with my boyfriend as soon as possible. We were alone in the room at night and I shared the happiness with my boyfriend and I told him that I was pregnant his child. I hugged him tightly, hoping he would be as happy as I was. He gave me very unexpected feedback to me. He was shocked when he heard the news and he was not ready to take all the responsibility after all this. He asked me to abort my baby. He destroyed me. He broke my heart so hard. I already refused his orders but he forced me violently, he slapped me, he punched me, even I was strangled by him, until my breath slowed down and I couldn't breathe anymore.
